		(layer "B.Cu")
		(uuid "2c3ac5b5-0264-4cb9-93c7-3bbc3ad2cd46")
		(at 45 96 180)
		(descr "Keystone 1043 THM holder for one 18650 Li-ion cell (leaf springs, PC pins). Body 77.1x20.7mm shared with the SMT 1042: identical diagonal Ø3.45 pegs at (±27.6, ∓8) and Ø2.39 index post at (-36.13, -8) — taken from the stock KiCad 1042 footprint. PC pins Ø1.19 on the battery axis at the ends: catalog THM mounting detail span 2.822in/71.6mm → ±35.8 (the stalled KiCad MR !2043 used ±36.11); drill enlarged to Ø2.6 (pad Ø4.2) so the pin fits under either reading. Pad 1 = same end as the 1042's pad 1 (left). VERIFY vs the Keystone 1043 drawing before fab.")
